data.description: Welcome Home to this adorable 3 bed, 2.5 bathroom home in Silver Pointe! This home an open concept featuring a family room with a cozy fireplace, an island kitchen -perfect for entertaining-with breakfast bar seating, tons of cabinetry & a dining room with a slider to your own fenced backyard! Upstairs you will find 2 secondary bedrooms & a bathroom along with your spacious primary featuring a large walk-in closet & full bath! This charming home has an attached 2 car garage and there is an athletic court & playground! You won't want to miss this one!
